[SPEAKER_01] koristiti

1080
01:03:00,139 --> 01:03:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] baš službeno

1081
01:03:01,519 --> 01:03:02,260
[SPEAKER_01] od crkve

1082
01:03:02,260 --> 01:03:03,820
[SPEAKER_01] ili u vrijeme

1083
01:03:03,820 --> 01:03:05,599
[SPEAKER_01] susreta molitvene zajednice

1084
01:03:05,599 --> 01:03:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] kad ćeš moći djelovati

1085
01:03:06,460 --> 01:03:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] u svoj karizmi

1086
01:03:07,239 --> 01:03:07,820
[SPEAKER_01] i na misiji.

1087
01:03:07,820 --> 01:03:09,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali većinom

1088
01:03:09,099 --> 01:03:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] je to alat

1089
01:03:10,340 --> 01:03:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] koji ti je dan

1090
01:03:11,039 --> 01:03:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] da ga koristiš

1091
01:03:12,000 --> 01:03:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] u svojoj svakodnevici

1092
01:03:13,000 --> 01:03:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] da bi tu svakodnevicu,

1093
01:03:14,340 --> 01:03:15,579
