1094
01:03:15,579 --> 01:03:16,559
[SPEAKER_01] svoju obitelj,

1095
01:03:16,559 --> 01:03:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] posao posvećivao

1096
01:03:17,760 --> 01:03:18,179
[SPEAKER_01] i dovodio

1097
